summary: This mod is a conversion of Ebony Catsuit standalone by comrade1280 to the CHSBHC body

----------------[IMG]http://i59.tinypic.com/2col8k3.jpg[/IMG]----------------

This mod is a conversion of Ebony Catsuit standalone by comrade1280 to the CHSBHC body.contains: weight slider, pauldrons-no pauldrons cuirass type. Armor can be crafted and upgradeable under Ebony section.
